        "description": {
            "value": "<p>A cacophonous noise blasts out, dealing 2d10 sonic damage. Each creature must attempt a Fortitude save.</p>\r<p>\n<hr><b>Critical Success</b>  The creature is unaffected.</p>\r<p>\n<b>Success</b>  The creature takes half damage.</p>\r<p>\n<b>Failure</b>  The creature takes full damage and is @Compendium[pf2e.conditionspf2e.9PR9y0bi4JPKnHPR]{Deafened} for 1 round.</p>\r<p>\n<b>Critical Failure</b>  The creature takes double damage, is @Compendium[pf2e.conditionspf2e.9PR9y0bi4JPKnHPR]{Deafened} for 1 minute, and is  @Compendium[pf2e.conditionspf2e.dfCMdR4wnpbYNTix]{Stunned} 1.</p>\r<p>\n<hr><b>Heightened (+1)</b>  The damage increases by 1d10.</p>",
